] 巴基斯坦总理伊姆兰·汗因腐败指控被判入狱——</b></span> <a class="link" href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2023/aug/05/former-pakistan-prime-minister-imran-khan-jailed-for-three-years" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">《卫报》</a></p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;">巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗被捕并被判处三年监禁，此前伊斯兰堡法院做出裁决，认定他犯有涉及出售国家礼品的“腐败行为”。汗被指控非法出售价值数亿卢比的礼物，导致他五年内失去政治资格。他否认有不当行为并计划上诉，而他的律师和支持者则认为审判不公平。这次逮捕可能会结束汗参加巴基斯坦即将举行的大选的机会。</p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:start;"><b>想阅读更多内容吗？</b></p><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:start;">请参阅<a class="link" href="https://www.newsminimalist.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">newsminimalist.com</a>上的其他新闻。</p><hr class="content_break"><p class="paragraph" style="text-align:start;"><i>感谢您阅读我们的文章，明天见，</i><br><i>新闻 极简主义</i></p></div><div class='beehiiv__footer'><br class='beehiiv__footer__break'><hr class='beehiiv__footer__line'> <a target="_blank" class="beehiiv__footer_link" style="text-align: center;" href="https://www.beehiiv.com/?utm_campaign=6cf225cc-836c-4b61-bc4c-5d29a9ac93b1&amp;utm_medium=post_rss&amp;utm_source=news_minimalist_daily">技术支持：beehiv</a></div></div> ]]>;</content:encoded></item><item><title> 8 月 5 日星期六——1 条重大新闻报道</title><description>大米价格上涨和饥饿危机</description><enclosure length="122256" type="image/png" url="https://media.beehiiv.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,quality=80/uploads/asset/file/96a08805-af63-4a0e-aadf-f3015b0f54af/template__3_.png"></enclosure><link/> https://newsletter.newsminimalist.com/p/saturday-august-5-1-significant-news-story<guid ispermalink="true"> https://newsletter.newsminimalist.com/p/saturday-august-5-1-significant-news-story</guid><pubDate> Sat, 05 Aug 2023 12:22:20 +0000</pubDate><atom:published> 2023-08-05T12:22:20Z </atom:published><content:encoded><![CDATA[
